 threatening to ban people or casting aspersions on their character PERHAPS they should take responsibility for their design flaws and simply fix the problem that they themselves have created.    <br><br>(... Actually, just see my post below, I already ranted about this, but I had to take another moment to laugh at Verant and their invincible Seru.) </p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
